quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  90,1,"Nay! I swear by this city",footnotes:182716:1,footnotes:182717:2
  90,2,"– this city wherein you have been rendered violable–",footnotes:182718:1
  90,3,"and I swear by the parent and his offspring:",footnotes:182719:1
  90,4,"Verily We have created man into toil and hardship.",footnotes:182720:1
  90,5,"Does he think that no one can overpower him?",footnotes:182721:1
  90,6,"He says: “I have squandered enormous wealth.”",footnotes:182722:1
  90,7,"Does he believe that none has seen him?",footnotes:182723:1
  90,8,"Did We not grant him two eyes,"
  90,9,"and a tongue and two lips?",footnotes:182724:1
  90,10,"And did We not show him the two highroads (of good and evil)?",footnotes:182725:1